#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag3.13:4.1"
msgid "3.13. Abhibhūtattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc255"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts255"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.13:5.1"
msgid "“Suṇātha ñātayo sabbe,"
msgstr "All my family gathered here,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:5.2"
msgid "yāvantettha samāgatā;"
msgstr "Listen to me,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:5.3"
msgid "Dhammaṃ vo desayissāmi,"
msgstr "I’ll teach you Dhamma!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:5.4"
msgid "dukkhā jāti punappunaṃ."
msgstr "Being born again and again is suffering."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.13:6.1"
msgid "<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^sn6.14#1 [14. Aruṇavatīsutta] | ^ne4#185 [Vibhaṅga/ Āvaṭṭahāravibhaṅga] | ^pe3#56 [Suttādhiṭṭhānatatiyabhūmi] | ^mi6.2.3#1 [Paṭipadādosapañha] | ^kv1.2#181 [Dutiyavagga/ Vacībhedakathā]\" id=\"note163\">*</span> <a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc256\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts256\"></a><span class=\"var\" title=\"ārabhatha (bj, s2, s3, pts1-2) | ārabbhatha (mr)\" id=\"note164\">Ārambhatha</span> nikkamatha,"
msgstr "Rouse yourselves, try harder!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:6.2"
msgid "Yuñjatha buddhasāsane;"
msgstr "Devote yourselves to the teachings of the Buddha!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:6.3"
msgid "Dhunātha maccuno senaṃ,"
msgstr "Crush the army of death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:6.4"
msgid "Naḷāgāraṃva kuñjaro."
msgstr "Like an elephant crushes a hut of reeds."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc257"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts257"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.13:7.1"
msgid "Yo imasmiṃ dhammavinaye,"
msgstr "Whoever will live heedfully"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:7.2"
msgid "appamatto <span class=\"var\" title=\"vihessati (bj, s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note165\">vihassati</span>;"
msgstr "In this Dhamma and discipline,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:7.3"
msgid "Pahāya jātisaṃsāraṃ,"
msgstr "Will abandon transmigration through births,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.13:7.4"
msgid "dukkhassantaṃ karissatī”ti."
msgstr "And make an end to suffering."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
